*lxd-0.16 (28 Aug 2015)

  28 Aug 2015; <erik@gentoo.org> +lxd-0.16.ebuild,
  +files/lxd-0.16-nc-binary-name.patch, +files/lxd-0.16.confd,
  +files/lxd-0.16.initd, +files/lxd.service, +metadata.xml:
  --tcp daemon option is deprecated. Add lvm and criu use flags to enable
  runtime features. Add daemon use flag, which when disabled builds only the
  client tool.

